01:28.440 --> 01:33.960
about certainly from a architecture perspective, so if you look at the slide that's in front

01:33.960 --> 01:39.640
of you right here, it really depicts what a typical architecture may look like, very

01:39.640 --> 01:45.360
simplified of course, but what a typical architecture may look like in any organization

01:45.360 --> 01:50.840
