04:54.520 --> 05:00.200
for example your parking lot or other buildings that may be next to you, so a better architecture

05:00.200 --> 05:06.200
would be the place that wireless access point in the middle of the building so that you can limit

05:06.200 --> 05:14.280
the signals and what they can reach to areas that you don't trust, now understanding something called

05:14.280 --> 05:21.640
the radio frequency spectrum allows us to understand why it's important for us to protect certain

05:21.640 --> 05:28.520
types of traffic that operate at frequencies within this wireless radio spectrum, so the ones that

