06:47.480 --> 06:54.280
problem is when you look at this entire radio frequency band there is really no security built in

06:54.280 --> 07:02.360
I mean the radio frequency band does not have any security built in therefore we need to add security

07:02.360 --> 07:11.560
if we want security of wireless and here are examples I mean Wi-Fi is the most obvious example

07:11.560 --> 07:17.240
of where we use radio frequencies that are wireless that do not have any security built in

