07:37.640 --> 07:44.760
so what you want to remember from this slide especially specifically is that if you want security

07:44.760 --> 07:51.720
to exist of anything that is wireless there are really four things that you need to address

07:51.720 --> 07:57.880
there are four security services that need to be addressed in anything that is wireless

07:57.880 --> 08:04.520
and it is what you see on the left hand side of this table right if you want security of wireless

08:04.520 --> 08:10.520
